X:9
T:IX - Crossing Scale (Bass to Treble)
C:Rodriguez Do Campo Method (2020)
M:4/4
L:1/8
Q:1/4=72
K:C
%%text Ascending scale crossing from bass to treble clef with hand replacement.
%%text RH descending: 4-3-2-1, LH ascending: 1-2-3-4. Apply permutations A-D.
V:1 clef=treble name="RH"
z8|z8|!accent!cdef !accent!gabc'|!accent!d'e'f'g' c'8|]
V:2 clef=bass name="LH"
!accent!C,D,E,F, !accent!G,A,B,C|!accent!DEFG !accent!ABcd|z8|z8|]
